        Public constructor of the Member class
        Parameters:
        id - The unique member ID.
        givenName - The first name of the member.
        familyName - The family name of the member.
        birthday - The day of birth formatted as year-month-day.
        memberSince - The day the member joined formatted as year-month-day.
        role - The members role, 0 = player, 1 = coach, 2 = parent.
        team - The name of the team, can be blank.
        gender - The gender of the member, 1 = male, 2 = female.
